'''《大同》'''（{{lang-en|The Chinese Mayor}}）原名'''中国市长'''（{{lang-en|Bulldozers, Paving Stones and Power: The Chinese Mayor}}），是[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]導演[[周浩_(导演)|周浩]]的第2部獲金馬獎的[[紀錄片|紀錄片]]<ref>{{cite news|author=宋馥李|title=大同的耿式难题|url=http://datong.house.qq.com/a/20150302/049510.htm|accessdate=2015-03-12|newspaper=经济观察报|date=2015-03-02|archive-date=2018-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628233416/http://datong.house.qq.com/a/20150302/049510.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此片榮獲[[第52屆金馬獎|第52屆金馬獎]][[金馬獎最佳紀錄片|最佳紀錄片]]<ref>{{cite news | title = 茉莉：從瑞典坼遷看中國「坼遷市長」 | publisher = 大紀元 | url = http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/8/3/n4494839.htm | date = 2015-08-13 | author = 高義 | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2020-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200120175120/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/8/3/n4494839.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 金馬獎／最佳紀錄片《大同》拍山西造鎮：金馬口味很寬 | publisher = 東森新聞 | url = http://star.ettoday.net/news/600925 | date = 2015-11-21 | author = 林映妤 | accessdate = 2015-11-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016145204/https://star.ettoday.net/news/600925 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 《灣生》落馬 網友質疑不符「一中」被做掉 | publisher = 自由時報 | url = http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1516240 | date = 2015-11-22 | author = 陳立妍 | accessdate = 2015-11-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2018-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181216195707/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1516240 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 3騎金馬放異彩 山西人好風光 | publisher = 中國時報 | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20151123000746-260309 | date = 2015-11-23 | author = 黃阡阡 | accessdate = 2015-11-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2021-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210215030649/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20151123000746-260309 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 塗翔文／台片豐收的表象背後 | publisher = 聯合報 | url = http://udn.com/news/story/7341/1330877 | date = 2015-11-21 | author = 塗翔文 | accessdate = 2015-11-22 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-10-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191014234225/https://udn.com/news/story/7341/1330877 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。講述[[山西省|山西]][[大同市|大同市]]前市長[[耿彥波|耿彥波]]2007年在大同大搞旧房[[拆迁|拆迁]]重建[[大同城墙|古城牆]]的事情。

